commit.title: Add support for parameters in "Add Ring" and "Add Field".
commit.message:
Add support for parameters in "Add Ring" and "Add Field".

Improve error messages and operation lookup

ring on opp involutive

Comment parametric rings

Add changelog

Improve error messages

Add power theory

If the parametric declaration has impargs, we use them for the auxiliary lemmas.

Note: We expect the domain to be invertible so that unification works.

Co-Authored-By: VincentSe
